{"tid":1763020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【踢爆寶福山大話連篇】錄音曾掦言無周梓樂資料 犯眾怒後急改口指誤會","createTime":"2019-11-30T04:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T19:14:19.000Z","uid":78546,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"15b1acc1ba866b942beb1f01ef2788f561c05561","tid":1763020,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:14:59.000Z","msg":"事實上，本刊接獲寶福山不做周梓樂家人出殯的消息後，曾致電寶福山查問，問負責人周梓樂是否將於寶福山出殯，對方說：「這裡暫時未有資料，我真的不知道他是否在這裡。（不是這裡？）我不知，我未有資料。（那我應該打去那個部門問？）寶福這個部門就是可以，我幫你看了，未有資料。如果你要知，你要問主家。」記者問：說是定了12月？「我怎麼知道，我現在跟你看過的資料就是沒有資料。」記者問道，你知哪位周梓樂嗎？他說：「知。周公個周，萬梓良個梓、快樂個樂。」他不願再多說，向記者道：「你問番主家吧。」<br />\n<br />\n據知，現時有兩間教會己答應幫手，周家上下正在考慮中，並不願意去寶福山。"},{"pid":"d2dfc73db6eb0406db8fd652820401f88f5dc08e","tid":1763020,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:15:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_711521_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_711521_0&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=fe081d92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_711521_0&h=da80d545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_711521_0</a>"},{"pid":"47b8e6ced245cab5cfb805972bfc7246d09b84f3","tid":1763020,"uid":810,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"如果我地真係炒車既<br />\n渣哥琴晚洗出黎幫周媽轉搵萬國搞?<br />\n用下個閪腦啦<br />\n人地講兩句話澄清你就信撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c692f93f81e5bf12ffd06fd1df6b21e7ffde917b","tid":1763020,"uid":78546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"47b8e6ced245c